snippet.title: Pogo Sticker v1.0.3 (Windows game 2005)
snippet.description:
Pogo Sticker is a platform game by Skinflake, Jetro Lauha.
The objective is to make the main player go to the finish location to the next level by using only your mouse.
If the main player lost the power of jumping and get too much damage (especially head), the game will be over.
